docs/source/screen-spec.md:12:| Primary Business Process | Member loan request, appraisal, sanction, documentation, disbursement, repayment, monitoring, default handling and closure |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:25:The screen specification converts the process into practical product screens that can be designed and built. It is intentionally detailed so that a product, design or engineering team can understand how the operational SOP should appear and behave in a working application.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:29:1. Policy and reference data configuration.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:31:3. Initial loan request.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:32:4. Application completeness checking.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:66:| Loan Origination | New application, application detail, completeness check, deficiency and rejection handling |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:69:| Documentation | Document checklist, PoA, tri-party agreement, SH-4, CDSL pledge, term sheet, loan agreement, bank verification letter |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:91:7. Mobile app borrower self-service unless separately prioritised. This spec assumes an internal web application with optional borrower-facing digital intake.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:133:- CDSL pledge incomplete for demat shares.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:163:| Application Reference Number | Starts at `LO00000001` and increments sequentially. Assigned after completeness check. |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:167:| Security Reference | SH-4 reference or CDSL Pledge Sequence Number. |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:175:- Deputy Manager - Finance: application completeness and appraisal preparation.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:178:- Compliance Team Member: document preparation and checklist management.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:184:- Internal Auditor: read-only access to complete audit trails and documents.
docs/source/screen-spec.md:197:| Global search | Search by borrower name, application number, loan account number, folio number, Aadhaar last four digits, PAN, SAP customer code, mobile number or security reference. |
docs/source/screen-spec.md:198:| Notification bell | Shows pending approvals, deficiencies, expiring TATs, overdue loans, compliance alerts. |
