+- Forbidden/protected paths will not be modified: `docs/source/**`, `scripts/**`, `.ralph/config.yaml`, `.ralph/permissions.json`, `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, `.gitignore`, high-risk/design/decision guardrails.
